  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis:

      Increased contact with the diabetes care team throughout pregnancy will lead to improved
      glucose control during pregnancy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patient will have weekly contact through the Mayo Patient On-line Services to send in their
      blood glucose readings and to receive recommendations back regarding insulin dose changes.
      Information will be analyzed regarding the magnitude of change in insulin dosing and in
      glycemic variability.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
